Package com.googlecode.cqengine.collection.impl

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConcurrentIndexedCollection<O>
    An implementation of Set which additionally wraps QueryEngineInternal, thus providing ConcurrentIndexedCollection.retrieve(com.googlecode.cqengine.query.Query) methods for performing queries on the collection to retrieve matching objects, and ConcurrentIndexedCollection.addIndex(com.googlecode.cqengine.index.Index) methods allowing indexes to be added to the collection to improve query performance.
    DefaultConcurrentSetFactory<O>
    Creates a concurrent implementation of a Set, based on ConcurrentHashMap.
    ObjectLockingIndexedCollection<O>
    Extends ConcurrentIndexedCollection with some specialized locking for applications in which multiple threads might try to add or remove the same object to/from an indexed collection concurrently.
